 {"id":"asupersync-1qfd0.35","title":"[audit][service] Make Oneshot transition safely if inner call panics","description":"ServiceExt::oneshot takes the request out of its Ready state before invoking service.call(req). If that synchronous call panics while constructing the inner future, a caught unwind leaves the Oneshot future stuck in Ready with request=None instead of moving to a terminal state. Patch src/service/service.rs so the panic path leaves Oneshot internally consistent, add a focused regression that catches the first panic and verifies the future is no longer poisoned with the wrong invariant, and validate with rch-backed targeted check/clippy/test commands.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"CyanDesert","estimated_minutes":45,"created_at":"2026-03-09T02:08:08.146146717Z","created_by":"CyanDesert","updated_at":"2026-03-09T02:18:12.319860801Z","closed_at":"2026-03-09T02:18:12.319834712Z","close_reason":"Completed","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["audit","service"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"asupersync-1qfd0.35","depends_on_id":"asupersync-1qfd0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-09T02:08:08.146146717Z","created_by":"CyanDesert","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
